{"tid":1164263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27歲無綫藝人郭子豪涉酒駕 神情嚴肅抵法院","createTime":"2019-05-21T02:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T04:42:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"44771d376b4e412208a68e41ddcf1f3417303e28","tid":1164263,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"27歲TVB藝人郭子豪（Arnold）早前涉酒駕被捕（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2wbYjWR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wbYjWR&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=b9d89f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2wbYjWR</a> ），在3月27日凌晨，警方於尖沙嘴梳士巴利道與麼地道交界設路障，進行打擊酒後駕駛行動，其間一名駕駛私家車的27歲姓郭男子，未能通過酒精呼氣測試，酒精呼氣測試顯示為50度，比法例上限22度超逾一倍而被警方以涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕，其後郭子豪表示不適，被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n案件今早於九龍城裁判法院提堂，郭子豪身穿黑色西裝配以藍色領帶出庭應訊，早上8時45分由公司經理人陪同到場，神情嚴肅，企定定讓傳媒拍攝時才展露微笑，不發一言便進入法院。<br />\n27歲郭子豪曾就讀喇沙書院及英國布萊頓公學，畢業於倫敦帝國學院機械工程系，2012年回港當模特兒，2014年讀第28期TVB藝訓班跳入公仔箱，同時幫父親經營自家服裝品牌及擔任私人健身教練，他憑電視劇《跳躍生命線》演救護員「陸昊然（六號）」而廣為觀眾認識，2018年奪得「第一屆華南地區男子運動模特組別冠軍」，成為首位在健美比賽中獲取冠軍的香港藝人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190521/large/1558402894_1cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190521%2Flarge%2F1558402894_1cbc.jpg&h=faaaa049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190521/59623708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59623708&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=45d0ba30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F59623708&h=bb613386\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190521/59623708</a>"},{"pid":"25236249aadeac61d82d7e75cc1ace0782af1f53","tid":1164263,"uid":60831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:54:00.000Z","msg":"笑死，當時仲唔認係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f083524ccffa824dc01eb3c36046649c56650ebb","tid":1164263,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"比起連登仔 呀豪都算有為 連登仔冇資格踩"},{"pid":"164365e78e1d29f2ba17a5cf233dc279b8278e54","tid":1164263,"uid":166908,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"屌佢個髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪剪緊嗰陣訓著咗比師傅一嘢剷落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabe322b9e85751f654b52face0aa5fe55258173","tid":1164263,"uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"又醉駕又想唔認 仆街到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bda4726b865aa342d20d0fc12edbd87ddcf56b6","tid":1164263,"uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"6239d3e04a784686d887dbb7ac1d18e71794bb2d","tid":1164263,"uid":7854,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/EkHbiqD1yu6Wc/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FEkHbiqD1yu6Wc%2Fgiphy.gif&h=bed9701a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e08b5e93d618e02b68a7a553210fc0fce5c10181","tid":1164263,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25236249aadeac61d82d7e75cc1ace0782af1f53","tid":1164263,"uid":60831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:54:00.000Z","msg":"笑死，當時仲唔認係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"讀咁多書，一d智慧都冇<img src=\"/asset